  "subject": "[PORTALNG] Add dedicated release job to publish bff jar",
  "commit_message": "[PORTALNG] Add dedicated release job to publish bff jar\n\n- before, each commit on main triggered the release job\n- now, each commit on main triggers a snapshot release job\n- releasing now becomes a conscious decision which replicates\n  the behaviour of the maven based release jobs\n  (via releases/release.yaml files)\n\nIssue-ID: PORTALNG-173\nChange-Id: I58b11ef5b7a1ad8eea8cced80a71c02bc5b4b669\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
